<p>To automatically upgrade from 2.7 to 2.7.1 Beta 1, change the version in your wp-includes/version.php file from 2.7 to 2.7.1-beta and then visit Tools-&gt;Upgrade.  Otherwise, <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/wordpress-2.7.1-beta1.zip\">download the beta package</a> and install manually.</p>
